    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>【成为扭曲之物后的故事】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">一夜之间，我变成了……万手一体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">以独特的视角体验噩梦循环，你只需要感受诡谲与疯狂。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>【混淆虚幻与现实的界限】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">用实景美术混淆虚幻与现实的界限，常见之物也能带来刺骨寒意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">自由搭配不同“器官‘，组成新的战术，让那些畸形之物带你走出梦境。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839810/extras/108021f429f5cb696036bd67dc0d8007.poster.avif?t=1770735075\" width=616 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839810/extras/108021f429f5cb696036bd67dc0d8007.webm?t=1770735075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839810/extras/108021f429f5cb696036bd67dc0d8007.mp4?t=1770735075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>【维持最后一丝理智去战斗】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">用残存的最后一丝理智战斗，对抗那些由扭曲回忆与负面情感组成的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在创新的卡牌战斗中，把所有物品都当作武器，冷静规划出牌顺序，选择优先清理威胁或是直接攻击敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839810/extras/44cff3fa64b453650e25f0a868e01018.poster.avif?t=1770735075\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839810/extras/44cff3fa64b453650e25f0a868e01018.webm?t=1770735075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839810/extras/44cff3fa64b453650e25f0a868e01018.mp4?t=1770735075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>【探寻异变背后的真相】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">和内在的自我对话，聆听神秘、逻辑、行动三种思维的低语，拼凑出混沌背后的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">或是，永远的活在梦魇之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839810/extras/0cda1245fef1f37f2e5e9ddd0246a5ee.poster.avif?t=1770735075\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839810/extras/0cda1245fef1f37f2e5e9ddd0246a5ee.webm?t=1770735075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839810/extras/0cda1245fef1f37f2e5e9ddd0246a5ee.mp4?t=1770735075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">P.S.本游戏中万手皆由开发者一人演绎，没有任何一只手在制作过程中受到伤害。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>作品荣誉：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">IGN中国 2025单机游戏年度评选 年度未来可期 获奖</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">第十三届金茶奖 2025年度优秀独立游戏 获奖</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">2025第五届中国游戏创新比赛 最佳创新设计奖 获奖</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">*2025第五届中国游戏创新大赛 最佳创新单机游戏奖 入围</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">2024美国IndieCade艺术节 开发者选择奖</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">*2024美国IndieCade艺术节 视觉设计奖 提名</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">2024日本京都BitSummit独立游戏展会 媒体选择奖</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">*GWB腾讯独立游戏大奖赛 2023 育碧单项奖 优秀叙事表达奖 提名</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">中国独立游戏大赛 2022 最佳创新 获奖</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">GWB独立游戏大奖赛 2022 最佳视觉风格 获奖</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">2021心动独立营 最佳游戏获奖</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">2021心动独立营 最佳创意获奖</p>",
